column2: SELECT TOP # p.objID, s.specObjID, s.ra, s.dec, s.cx, s.cy, s.cz, -- s.z as redshift, s.zErr. s.zWarning, s.subClass -- s.z_noqso, s.zErr_noqso. s.zWarning_noqso p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.extinction_u, p.extinction_g, p.extinction_r, p.extinction_i, p.extinction_z, p.err_u, p.err_g, p.err_r, p.err_i, p.err_z, s.survey, s.instrument, s.programname, s.spectrographID from PhotoObj as p JOIN SpecObj as s ON s.bestObjID = p.objID
